                        <p>f'(c) = lim<sub>hâ†’0</sub> [f(c + h) - f(c)] / h</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="rule-box">
                        <p><strong>2. Turunan Konstan:</strong></p>
                        <p>Jika f(x) = k, maka f'(x) = 0</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="rule-box">
                        <p><strong>3. Aturan Rantai:</strong></p>
                        <p>dy/dx = (dy/du) Â· (du/dx)</p>
                    </div>
                </section>

